ACH_Code__c.inlineHelpText: The Standard Entry Class (SEC) code used for this ACH transaction.
ACH_Code__c.label: ACH Code

ACH_Last_4__c.inlineHelpText: The last four digits of the bank account used for this transaction.
ACH_Last_4__c.label: ACH Last 4

Authorized_Date__c.inlineHelpText: The date and time the transaction was authorized.
Authorized_Date__c.label: Authorized Date

Authorized_UTC_Timestamp__c.inlineHelpText: The exact date and time (down to the millisecond) from the payment gateway that this transaction was successfully authorized.
Authorized_UTC_Timestamp__c.label: Authorized UTC Timestamp

Batch_Number__c.inlineHelpText: The batch that set this Payment as paid. This field is automatically populated based on your Batch Number Settings in NPSP Settings.
Batch_Number__c.label: Batch Number

Card_Expiration_Month__c.inlineHelpText: The expiration month of the card used for this transaction.
Card_Expiration_Month__c.label: Card Expiration Month

Card_Expiration_Year__c.inlineHelpText: The expiration year of the card used for this transaction.
Card_Expiration_Year__c.label: Card Expiration Year

Card_Last_4__c.inlineHelpText: The last four digits of the card used for this transaction.
Card_Last_4__c.label: Card Last 4

Card_Network__c.inlineHelpText: The card network of the card used for this transaction.
Card_Network__c.label: Card Network

Donor_Cover_Amount__c.inlineHelpText: The amount the donor paid in addition to their donation amount, often to help cover transaction fees or to add a tip to their donation.
Donor_Cover_Amount__c.label: Donor Cover Amount

Elevate_Original_Payment_ID__c.inlineHelpText: For refunds only. Shows the ID of the original payment transaction from Elevate.
Elevate_Original_Payment_ID__c.label: Elevate Original Payment ID

Elevate_Payment_API_Declined_Reason__c.inlineHelpText: Provides detail about why a transaction was declined.
Elevate_Payment_API_Declined_Reason__c.label: Elevate Payment API Declined Reason

Elevate_Payment_API_Status__c.inlineHelpText: The API status value for this Elevate connected Payment record.
Elevate_Payment_API_Status__c.label: Elevate Payment API Status

Elevate_Payment_Created_Date__c.inlineHelpText: The date and time the transaction was created.
Elevate_Payment_Created_Date__c.label: Elevate Payment Created Date

Elevate_Payment_Created_UTC_Timestamp__c.inlineHelpText: The exact date and time (down to the millisecond) from Elevate that the transaction was created.
Elevate_Payment_Created_UTC_Timestamp__c.label: Elevate Payment Created  UTC Timestamp

Elevate_Payment_ID__c.inlineHelpText: The unique ID for this transaction from Elevate.
Elevate_Payment_ID__c.label: Elevate Payment ID

Elevate_Transaction_Fee__c.inlineHelpText: The transaction fee charged by Elevate.
Elevate_Transaction_Fee__c.label: Elevate Transaction Fee

Gateway_ID__c.inlineHelpText: The ID of the payment gateway that processed this transaction.
Gateway_ID__c.label: Gateway ID

Gateway_Payment_ID__c.inlineHelpText: The unique ID for this transaction from the payment gateway.
Gateway_Payment_ID__c.label: Gateway Payment ID

Gateway_Transaction_Fee__c.inlineHelpText: The transaction fee charged by your payment gateway.
Gateway_Transaction_Fee__c.label: Gateway Transaction Fee

Origin_ID__c.inlineHelpText: The ID for the system where the transaction was initiated.
Origin_ID__c.label: Origin ID

Origin_Name__c.inlineHelpText: The name of the system where the transaction was initiated.
Origin_Name__c.label: Origin Name

Origin_Type__c.inlineHelpText: The type of system used to initiate the transaction. Available values include Engagement Hub, Giving Page, Payments API, Salesforce.
Origin_Type__c.label: Origin Type

Payment_Acknowledgment_Status__c.inlineHelpText: Status of Acknowledgment of this payment.
Payment_Acknowledgment_Status__c.label: Payment Acknowledgment Status

Total_Transaction_Fees__c.inlineHelpText: The sum of the transaction fees charged by Elevate and your payment gateway.
Total_Transaction_Fees__c.label: Total Transaction Fees
